{"tid":1493437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［必須正視］拒絕任何平台 只接受直接回應五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-21T08:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T12:05:13.000Z","uid":55257,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"07c8e63168859cca2fca232015a858e2aa8f27f4","tid":1493437,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥未有回應反修例人士的五大訴求之時，宣佈會積極與「有心人」建立溝通平台。據了解，林鄭已向約20至30位不同界別，包括政界、宗教界及教育界等代表發出會面邀請，邀約於本周六首度會面，當中包括曾稱願意協助舉辦對話平台、擔當主持的前政務司司長唐英年、一直提倡獨立調查的前運房局局長張炳良、至少兩位大學校長包括教大校長張仁良及浸大校長錢大康，以及天主教香港教區宗座署理湯漢等。上述各人都支持各界對話，加深了解，達致社會和解。曾於2014年傘運時代表學聯與時任政務司司長林鄭月娥對話的岑敖暉指，從溝通人選反映政府無意解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190821/59956057?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F59956057%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9orrngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=e3365708\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F59956057%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=dc3479a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190821/59956057?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"a09083ba15abec310029e4ca7076e718adc1331d","tid":1493437,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfc3d4cf8d26d5f1d062aebf4865ff05abb3019","tid":1493437,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-